ormal"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: justify;"&gt;               &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0cm; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; text-indent: 0cm;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US"&gt;Â·&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US"&gt;"Writing is a confidence trick you play on yourselfâ¦ and one which you must perpetuate on a daily basis.â&lt;i&gt; &lt;/i&gt;Iâm not sure who said that, but I love it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Georgia; mso-bidi-font-family: Times; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background: white; line-height: 12.0pt; margin-left: 36.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 36.0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; mso-pagination: none; text-autospace: none; text-indent: -18.0pt;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;What is your work in progress? Tell us about it.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;Iâm currently wrapping up work on the second book in the series, &lt;i&gt;Heroes &amp;amp; Hooligans in Goose Pimple Junction. &lt;/i&gt;The mc in this book is Martha Maye, one of the secondary characters in &lt;i&gt;Murder &amp;amp; Mayhem&lt;/i&gt;. Her divorce is about to become final when her philandering husband comes to town, claiming to be a changed man (we all know how that usually works out) and attempting to woo her back â until heâs murdered. Also in town are a serial thief, a stalker, and a murderer, who are all making the townsfolk anxious and keeping the handsome new police chief as busy as a moth in a mitten.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;What are your thoughts on self-publishing verses traditional publishing?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;I think itâs great that authors have the option of self-publishing. If done professionally, authors can accomplish the same thing as many small imprints, yet they can reap all the profit. You definitely have to do your homework, and you shouldnât do everything on your own (e.g. editing, proofreading), but self-publishing can be empowering and exciting. Now, having said that, if a traditional publisher wants to publish my book, Iâm available for a conversation!&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US"&gt;What are you currently reading?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;I âreadâ a lot of audio books when Iâm driving or puttering around the house. Right now Iâm listening to &lt;i&gt;Hounded&lt;/i&gt;, by David Rosenfelt. Itâs number &lt;st1:metricconverter productid="11 in" w:st="on"&gt;11 in&lt;/st1:metricconverter&gt;his &lt;i&gt;Andy Carpenter&lt;/i&gt; series, and Iâve read and loved them all.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;On Kindle, Iâm reading book number &lt;st1:metricconverter productid="3 in" w:st="on"&gt;3 in&lt;/st1:metricconverter&gt; the &lt;i&gt;Jazz Age Mystery&lt;/i&gt; series, Gold Diggers, Gamblers and Guns, by Ellen Mansoor Collier.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;When youâre not writing, how do you spend your time?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;Photography is a hobby, as is putting together photography coffee table-type books. Iâm learning to use InDesign, and I plan to self-publish some of my work. I also love to bake, and spending time with my two sons, daughter-in-law, and two granddogs is a priority â whenever theyâll have me. And at the moment, Iâm busy looking for a house to buy and packing boxes. By the time this interview posts, hopefully I will have moved and will be unpacking said boxes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-GB"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.jolinsdell.com/" title="Jo Linsdell"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;img alt="blogsignatureWA" src="http://farm9.staticflickr.com/8176/8030439972_551fda411e.jpg" height="120" width="500" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;script src="//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js#pubid=xa-51adb6a4646b451d" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;document.doAT = function(cl) {         var myclass = new RegExp('hentry');         var myTitleContainer = new RegExp('post-title');         var myPostContent = new RegExp('post-footer');         var elem = this.getElementsByTagName('div');            var url;         var title = "";                  for (var i = 0; i &lt; elem.length; i++)         {             var classes = elem[i].className;             if (myclass.test(classes))             {                 var container = elem[i];              url = window.location.href;                               for (var b = 0; b &lt; container.childNodes.length; b++)                 {                     var item = container.childNodes[b].className;                     if (myTitleContainer.test(item))                     {                         var link = container.childNodes[b].getElementsByTagName('a');                         if (typeof(link[0]) != 'undefined')                         {                             var url = link[0].href;                             var title = link[0].innerHTML;                         }                      var singleq = new RegExp("'", 'g');                     var doubleq = new RegExp('"', 'g');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             title = title.replace(singleq, ''', 'gi');                     title = title.replace(doubleq, '"', 'gi');                      }                     if (myPostContent.test(item))                     {                         var footer = container.childNodes[b];                     }                 }                  var n = document.createElement('div');                  var at = "&lt;div class='addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style ' addthis:title='"+title+"' addthis:url='"+encodeURI(url)+"'   &gt; &lt;a class='addthis_button_facebook_like' fb:like:layout='button_count'&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class='addthis_button_tweet'&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class='addthis_button_pinterest_pinit'&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class='addthis_counter addthis_pill_style'&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;";                  n.innerHTML = at;                  container.insertBefore(n , footer);                }         }     return true; };  document.doAT('hentry'); &lt;/script&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitt