p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;There is no time to waste no time to wait&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;But I found that it is a âthin line between Love and Hateâ&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;I disregarded the warning signs and the clues&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Damn Iâm tired of getting this bad news&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;I guess karma is saying boy âyou paid your duesâ &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;She had me thinking we were coasting&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Come to find out she had mixed emotions &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Wow that chick had me real open&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Did I have some wrong preconceived notions&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Did I move to slow or too fast&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Forgive me for even trying to make it last.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Thought you were my everything I would for you do anything&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;The first time I swallowed my pride &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Yet bitterness you did keep inside&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;The second time I did not know what to do &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Still my heart and soul you never knew&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;This is it its over and Iâm thru&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Cause I know that thereâs life after you.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;For a minute it seems were one &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Then suddenly our honeymoon was done &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Fussing, fighting, moaning and groaning &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Stressing and strifing all day and all night&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Guess you couldnât hide your spots, lies, and stripes &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;We came a long way and gone so far&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="MsoNormalTable"&gt; &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;  &lt;td style="padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;"&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;But now Iâm getting out this damn car &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;When were together I stayed true &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;But now I now there is life after you&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;  &lt;td style="padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;"&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;You really had me going thinking we were going a certain way &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Iâm just glad it was only 8 months because Iâm good today &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;You didnât give me no explanation &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;I guess you still want to play &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;I guess you forgot about tomorrow as we lay&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;You did some good but lies wiped that all away&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Cant trust, listen, or love you cause I cant believe nothing you say&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Donât have to give me the cold shoulder&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;Iâm gone and Iâm glad that its over&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-q-7flKhvYEY/VDu3PxXd9JI/AAAAAAAAR24/Yh6wUEzTBRQ/s1600/hardlovebanner.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-q-7flKhvYEY/VDu3PxXd9JI/AAAAAAAAR24/Yh6wUEzTBRQ/s1600/hardlovebanner.jpg" height="205" width="320" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;script src="//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js#pubid=xa-51adb6a4646b451d" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;document.doAT = function(cl) {         var myclass = new RegExp('hentry');         var myTitleContainer = new RegExp('post-title');         var myPostContent = new RegExp('post-footer');         var elem = this.getElementsByTagName('div');            var url;         var title = "";                  for (var i = 0; i &lt; elem.length; i++)         {             var classes = elem[i].className;             if (myclass.test(classes))             {                 var container = elem[i];              url = window.location.href;                               for (var b = 0; b &lt; container.childNodes.length; b++)                 {                     var item = container.childNodes[b].className;                     if (myTitleContainer.test(item))                     {                         var link = container.childNodes[b].getElementsByTagName('a');                         if (typeof(link[0]) != 'undefined')                         {                             var url = link[0].href;                             var title = link[0].innerHTML;                         }                      var singleq = new RegExp("'", 'g');                     var doubleq = new RegExp('"', 'g');                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             title = title.replace(singleq, ''', 'gi');                     title = title.replace(doubleq, '"', 'gi');                      }                     if (myPostContent.test(item))                     {                         var footer = container.childNodes[b];                     }                 }                  var n = document.createElement('div');                  var at = "&lt;div class='addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style ' addthis:title='"+title+"' addthis:url='"+encodeURI(url)+"'   &gt; &lt;a class='addthis_button_facebook_like' fb:like:layout='button_count'&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class='addthis_button_tweet'&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class='addthis_button_pinterest_pinit'&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class='addthis_counter addthis_pill_style'&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;";                  n.innerHTML = at;                  container.insertBefore(n , footer);                }         }     return true; };  document.doAT('hentry'); &lt;/script&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.jolinsdell.com/" title="Jo Linsdell"&gt;&lt;img alt="blogsignatureWA" src="http://farm9.staticflickr.com/8176/8030439972_551fda411e.jpg" height="120" width="500" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-coun